https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sNPng6MmOALkDQepUv2LJbemTdr.jpg Crosby, Stills, & Nash join forces for their first live performance video in over 2 decades! Filmed during their 2012 tour, CSN 2012 includes many of the trio's classic hits, some new and unreleased songs, and a rare performance of "Suite: Judy Blue Eyes." The disc also includes 'A Conversation with David, Stephen and Graham,' plus interviews with their band and crew. A must-have for any CSN fan. Crosby, Stills & Nash - CSN 2012
